I"Ë<p><em>La Lucha Sin Fin: On Charisma and Its Persuasive Technologies</em> investigates the aesthetics of charisma and its persuasive technologies. From the megaphone, to the telephone, to television, to the web, virtually every technological advance has altered the mode of transmission for persuasion. The book explores the changing role of charisma as it is decoupled from physical presence and finds its way into the mediated channels of the internet.</p>
